title: Fantastic 3BR 1.5 BA Rambler
posting_body: ['5413 45th Ave N Robbinsdale, MN 55422', 'Price: $1750.00', 'Deposit: $1750.00', 'Fantastic 3BR 1.5 BA Rambler with huge 4 car heated garage!', 'The property offers 3 BRs on one level, gleaming hardwood floors and finished lower level with a cozy fireplace.', 'Great location with easy commute just about anywhere in the cities.', 'Very nice yard, with a storage shed, and a sweet garage.', 'Available now – 12 or 18 month lease terms.', 'Tenant pays all utilities (water/sewer, trash, gas and electric) and tenant is responsible for snow/lawn care and sprinkler maintenance.', 'Cats/Dogs OK max of 2 under 35 lbs.', 'w/$250 refundable pets deposit per pet.', 'No aggressive breeds, no puppies.', 'No birds.', 'Every pet/animal must go through professional screening process and apply.', 'The fee is $20 for the 1st pet and $15 for each additional, if applicable paid directly to the 3rd party screening vendor.', '$20/pet app fee paid at time of move in.', 'Non-refundable application Fee: $45/adult.', 'Information deemed reliable but guaranteed.', 'Renters insurance required.', 'Section 8 not approved.', 'Pet Policy: Cats/Dogs OK max of 2 under 35 lbs.', 'w/$250 refundable pets deposit per pet.', 'No aggressive breeds, no puppies.', 'No birds.', 'Every pet/animal must go through professional screening process and apply.', 'The fee is $20 for the 1st pet and $15 for each additional, if applicable paid directly to the 3rd party screening vendor.', '$20/pet app fee paid at time of move in.', 'Property Features', 'Single Family Home', '3 bed', '1.5 bath', 'Built 1953', '4 Parking Spaces', 'Land is 0.21 square', 'Floor Area is 1,463 square', '4 Garage', 'Ducted Heating', 'Ducted Cooling', 'Attached Garage', 'Fireplace', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Hennepin County', 'Storage Shed', 'Visit our website at <URL> for more information.']
